            <article id="about">
                <h3>About Us</h3>
                <div class="title-underline"></div>
                <div class="about-us">

                    <p class="motto">"If you build it, they will come".</p>
                    <p>We intend to use our considerable business and technical expertise to build Blockchain solutions which are geared towards the needs of our customers, and which will be thoroughly tested using the latest ideas in automation.</p>
                    <p>We also believe that Blockchain should only be used where it is demonstrably better than legacy technologies, and we are not afraid to mix the new components and tools with existing frameworks where we believe that to be appropriate.</p>
